## Code Sources and Inspirations

The following core technologies and code patterns were referenced during development:

- React component structure and hooks based on official React documentation [2].
- Tailwind CSS utility classes and responsive design patterns [3].
- Nginx server configuration and reverse proxy setup [4].
- Let's Encrypt SSL certificate automation using Certbot [6].
- AWS EC2 instance configuration and security group management [5].
- Weather data fetching logic inspired by Bureau of Meteorology public JSON endpoints [8] and Open-Meteo API [9].

**Note:** All code was manually reviewed, modified, and integrated by the developer. AI tools were used only for initial scaffolding and learning acceleration.
